<p>A Halifax Shopping Centre MasterCard © is good for an endless number of choices! Available in any denomination from $10 and up, it always fits your budget, and their style.</p>
<p>Halifax Shopping Centre Mastercards © can be purchased at Customer Service, as well as  <a href="#" onclick="window.open('http://halifax.storecardsonline.com','_blank','width=600,height=750,status=1,toolbar=1,scrollbars=1,resizable=1');">online</a>.</p>
