</div>
<div class="clearafter">&nbsp;</div>
<p>You can check the balance of your Halifax Shopping Centre MasterCard © online, or over the phone!</p>
<p>*Please Note cards purchased before February 1st, 2010 are unaffected by the changes in legislation made by the Government of Nova Scotia and can still be redeemed at Halifax Shopping Centre Retailers*</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<hr>
<p><a name="faqs"></a></p>
<h2>FAQs</h2>
<p>Here are some Frequently Asked Questions that will assist you in purchasing and using our New Halifax Shopping Centre MasterCard&reg; Gift Cards.</p>
<div id="myAccordion" class="accordion">
<div class="accordion-group">
<div class="accordion-heading">
<h5><a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#myAccordion" href="#collapseOne" class="accordion-toggle">1. Where and how do I buy Halifax Shopping Centre MasterCard® Gift Cards?</a></h5>
</div>
<div id="collapseOne" class="accordion-body collapse">
<div class="accordion-inner">
<p>Halifax Shopping Centre MasterCard® Gift Cards can be purchased in any denomination from $10 to $500 at our Guest Services during mall hours or online at <a href="www.halifaxshoppingcentre.com" target = "_blank">www.halifaxshoppingcentre.com</a>.  Our Guest Services desk is located on the lower level across from La Senza. Cash, debit card, VISA, and MasterCard are accepted forms of payment.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="accordion-group">
<div class="accordion-heading">
<h5><a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#myAccordion" href="#collapseTwo" class="accordion-toggle">2. Does the Halifax Shopping Centre MasterCard® Gift Card Expire?</a></h5>
</div>
<div id="collapseTwo" class="accordion-body collapse">
<div class="accordion-inner">
<p>Your Halifax Shopping Centre MasterCard® Gift Card will never expire. However, if there is a remaining balance on the card after the magnetic stripe has expired (there is an expiry date printed on the front of each Gift Card) similar to a credit card security feature, please visit our Guest Services location for a card </p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="accordion-group">
<div class="accordion-heading">
<h5><a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#myAccordion" href="#collapse3" class="accordion-toggle">3. Does the Halifax Shopping Centre MasterCard® have any maintenance fees?</a></h5>
</div>
<div id="collapse3" class="accordion-body collapse">
<div class="accordion-inner">
<p>A monthly maintenance fee of $2.50 is only deducted when there is a balance left on the card 16 months after its activation date. You may have the maintenance free period extended to 19 months by requesting an extension in the 15 month. Requests can be directed to 1-800-840-5604.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="accordion-group">
<div class="accordion-heading">
<h5><a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#myAccordion" href="#collapse4" class="accordion-toggle">4. Where can Halifax Shopping Centre MasterCard® Gift Cards be used?</a></h5>
</div>
<div id="collapse4" class="accordion-body collapse">
<div class="accordion-inner">
<p>Halifax Shopping Centre MasterCard® Gift Cards can be used at almost all Halifax Shopping Centre and Halifax Shopping Centre Annex retailers including Sears, Wal-Mart, Sobeys, Winners, Sears Outlet, and Pier I Imports.</p>
<p>Halifax Shopping Centre MasterCard® Gift Cards are currently not accepted at: BellAliant for bill payments, Atlantic Dental, Eastlink, Atlantic Lotto, Maritime Travel, and Subway. </p>
<p>Sears will accept the Halifax Shopping Centre MasterCard® Gift Card providing the gift card balance is greater than the Sears purchase amount. Sears point of sale system does not allow two methods of payment( ie: gift card and cash/visa/debit).</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="accordion-group">
<div class="accordion-heading">
<h5><a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#myAccordion" href="#collapse5" class="accordion-toggle">5. How do I use the Halifax Shopping Centre MasterCard® Gift Card?</a></h5>
</div>
<div id="collapse5" class="accordion-body collapse">
<div class="accordion-inner">
<p>Before you start shopping make sure the store accepts Halifax Shopping Centre MasterCard® Gift Cards. If the answer is yes, before ringing through your purchase, let the sales associate know you are using a Halifax Shopping Centre Mastercard Gift Card. Also make sure the store knows what the balance is on the gift card.</p>

</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="accordion-group">
<div class="accordion-heading">
<h5><a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#myAccordion" href="#collapse6" class="accordion-toggle">6. How Can I check the balance on my Halifax Shopping Centre MasterCard® Gift Card?</a></h5>
</div>
<div id="collapse6" class="accordion-body collapse">
<div class="accordion-inner">
<p>To check your gift card balance you can call 1-800-755-8608 24 hours a day,  or visit www.getmybalance.com. You can also visit the Halifax Shopping Centre Guest Services during mall hours. </p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="accordion-group">
<div class="accordion-heading">
<h5><a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#myAccordion" href="#collapse7" class="accordion-toggle">7. Can I add more money to my Halifax Shopping Centre MasterCard® Gift Card?</a></h5>
</div>
<div id="collapse7" class="accordion-body collapse">
<div class="accordion-inner">
<p>For security purposes the Halifax Shopping Centre MasterCard® Gift Card cannot be reloaded.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="accordion-group">
<div class="accordion-heading">
<h5><a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#myAccordion" href="#collapse8" class="accordion-toggle">8. What if I want to return the purchase I made using a Halifax Shopping Centre MasterCard® Gift Card?</a></h5>
</div>
<div id="collapse8" class="accordion-body collapse">
<div class="accordion-inner">
<p>Depending on the retailer’s return policy, you may receive a store credit, or where permitted a refund on merchandise can be credited to the Gift Card.  You should keep the gift card until you know a refund will not be required. A refund to the Halifax Shopping Centre MasterCard® Gift Card may  take 3 to 7 business days before the credit appears.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="accordion-group">
<div class="accordion-heading">
<h5><a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#myAccordion" href="#collapse9" class="accordion-toggle">9. What if my Halifax Shopping Centre MasterCard® Gift Card is lost or stolen?</a></h5>
</div>
<div id="collapse9" class="accordion-body collapse">
<div class="accordion-inner">
<p>Make sure you keep your receipt in case your Halifax Shopping Centre MasterCard® Gift Card is lost or stolen. Providing you have your receipt, the remaining balance can be locked and transferred onto a new card.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="accordion-group">
<div class="accordion-heading">
<h5><a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#myAccordion" href="#collapse10" class="accordion-toggle">10. Corporate Orders</a></h5>
</div>
<div id="collapse10" class="accordion-body collapse">
<div class="accordion-inner">
<p>If you are interested in a Corporate order please contact Allyson Boyd, Halifax Shopping Centre Guest Services Supervisor, Monday to Friday from 8:30am to 5pm at (902) 454-8666 or aboyd@20vic.com. She will be happy to prepare your order and have it available for pick up at either our Management Office or our Guest Services location.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="accordion-group">
<div class="accordion-heading">
<h5><a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#myAccordion" href="#collapse11" class="accordion-toggle">11. Will my old Halifax Shopping Centre gift cards still be honored?</a></h5>
</div>
<div id="collapse11" class="accordion-body collapse">
<div class="accordion-inner">
<p>Yes, all Halifax Shopping Centre Gift Cards will be accepted at participating retailers</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
